# API Endpoints Documentation

## Auth

* POST /auth/register — register a new user
* GET /auth/confirm-email — confirm user email via token
* POST /auth/login — authenticate user and return access token
* POST /auth/logout — logout user and invalidate token
* POST /auth/forgot-password — request password reset email
* POST /auth/reset-password — reset user password using token

---

## Users

* GET /users/profile — get current user profile
* PUT /users/update — update current user
* DELETE /users/delete — delete current user

---

## Specialists

* POST /specialists/create — create specialist profile
* GET /specialists/get/{specialist_id} — get specialist by ID
* PUT /specialists/update/{specialist_id} — update specialist profile
* PATCH /specialists/deactivate/{specialist_id} — deactivate specialist (admin)
* PATCH /specialists/verify/{specialist_id} — verify specialist (admin)
* DELETE /specialists/delete — delete current specialist
* GET /specialists/search — find specialists by location and filters

---

## Catalog

* POST /catalog/add/item — create catalog item
* GET /catalog/get/catalog/{specialist_id} — get specialist catalog
* PUT /catalog/update/{catalog_id} — update catalog item
* DELETE /catalog/delete/{catalog_id} — delete catalog item

---

## Address

* POST /address/add/address — create user address
* GET /address/get/address — get user address
* DELETE /address/delete/address — delete user address

---

## Files (Avatar)

* POST /files/upload/avatar — upload specialist avatar
* GET /files/get/avatar — get specialist avatar
* DELETE /files/delete/avatar — delete specialist avatar

---

## Files (Accreditation)

* POST /files/upload/accreditation — upload accreditation PDF
* GET /files/get/accreditation — get accreditation PDF
* DELETE /files/delete/accreditation — delete accreditation

---

## Orders

* POST /orders/create — create new order
* GET /orders/get/{order_id} — get order by ID
* GET /orders/my — get current user orders
* GET /orders/active — get active orders (for specialists)
* GET /orders/specialist/my — get specialist orders
* PUT /orders/update/{order_id} — update order
* POST /orders/take/{order_id} — request to take order
* POST /orders/complete/{order_id} — complete order
* POST /orders/cancel/{order_id} — cancel order
* DELETE /orders/delete/{order_id} — delete order

---

## Order Requests

* GET /requests/get/all — get all requests for current user
* PUT /requests/approve/{request_id} — approve order request

---

## Comments

* POST /comment/write — create comment for specialist
* GET /comment/get/comments — get comments list
* DELETE /comment/delete/{specialist_id} — delete comment

---

## Rates

* POST /rate/create — rate specialist
* GET /rate/get/rate/{specialist_id} — get specialist average rating
* DELETE /rate/delete/{specialist_id} — delete rating

---

## Messages

* POST /message/write — send message in order chat
* GET /message/get/chat/{order_id} — get messages for order chat
